Log Levels in printk
-------------------------------------
| Level          | Meaning          |
| -------------- | ---------------- |
| `KERN_EMERG`   | System crash     |
| `KERN_ALERT`   | Immediate action |
| `KERN_ERR`     | Error            |
| `KERN_WARNING` | Warning          |
| `KERN_NOTICE`  | Notice           |
| `KERN_INFO`    | Information      |
| `KERN_DEBUG`   | Debug            |
-------------------------------------
